pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">获取当前显示的样式</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"js\" spellcheck=\"false\">getComputedStyle(box1, null).backgroundColor\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">DOM获取其他样式</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"js\" spellcheck=\"false\">1. clientWidth: \n   clientHeight 获取元素的可见宽度和高度，但是只包括内容区和内边距\n2. offsetWidth:\n   offsetHeight； 获取元素的整个宽度和高度\n3. offsetParent\n   用来获取当前元素的定位父元素，找最近的那个\n4. offsetLeft:\n 	offsetTop: 当前元素相对于其定位父元素的水平和垂直偏移量\n5. scrollLeft:\n	scrollTop: 水平和垂直滚动条滚动的距离\n6. scrollHeight\n 	scrollWidth: 滚动条的长度\n  scrollHeight - scrollTop == clientHeight\n说明垂直滚动条滚动到底了\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">事件对象</span></h3>\n<figure class=\"md-table-fig\" style=\"margin: 1.2em 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; cursor: default; -ms-overflow-x: auto; max-width: calc(100% + 16px); box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<table class=\"md-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"md-end-block\">\n<th><span class=\"td-span\"><span class=\"md-plain\">事件对象</span></span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"md-end-block\">\n<td><span class=\"td-span\"><span class=\"md-plain\">当事件的响应函数被触发时，浏览器每次都会将一个事件对象作为实参传递进响应函数</span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"md-end-block\">\n<td><span class=\"td-span\"><span class=\"md-plain\">在事件对象中封装了当前事件相关的一切信息，比如：鼠标的坐标&nbsp; 键盘哪个按键被按下&nbsp; 鼠标滚轮滚动的方向</span></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</figure>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"js\" spellcheck=\"false\">window.onload = function(){\n    box1.onmousemove = function(event){\n        event = event || window.event;\n        var x = event.clientX;\n        var y  = event.clientY;\n        box2.innerHTML = x + \" , \" + y;\n    }\n}\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">设置盒子跟随鼠标移动</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"js\" spellcheck=\"false\">window.onload = function(){\n    var box1 = document.getElementById(\"box1\");\n\n    document.onmousemove = function(event){\n        //以下三句为了兼容性\n        event = event || window.event;\n\n        var st = document.body.scrollTop || document.documentElement.scrollTop;\n        var sl = document.body.scrollLeft || document.documentElement.scrollLeft;\n\n        var left = event.clientX;       //clientX只是代表当前窗口的偏移量 ，不是整个页面的\n        var top = event.clientY;\n\n        box1.style.left = left + sl + \"px\";\n        box1.style.top = top + st + \"px\"; \n    }\n}\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-in