.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">盒子模型</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"css\" spellcheck=\"false\">border: solid dotted dashed\nborder-collapse: collapse //将相邻的表格边框合并\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">给盒子添加边框会影响盒子的实际大小</span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">padding会影响盒子大小， 会撑大盒子，所以实际中可能要用盒子宽度-内边距，但如果盒子没有指定宽高，不会撑开盒子</span></h3>\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px; color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 4; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">继承的元素如果继承了父元素的宽高， 但是如果继承的元素内部没有写宽高， 那么在继承的元素内部写padding,也不会撑大继承元素的宽高，继承元素的宽高依旧和父元素一样。</span></p>\n<h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">新浪导航栏案例</span></h4>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">&lt;style&gt;\n        .nav{\n            height: 41px;\n            background-color: #fcfcfc;\n            border-top: 3px #ff8500 solid;\n            border-bottom: 1px #edeef0 solid;\n            font-size: 18px;\n\n        }\n        .nav a{\n            display: inline-block;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #4c4c4c;\n            line-height: 41px;\n            padding-left: 20px;\n            padding-right: 20px;\n            height: 41px;\n\n        }\n        .nav a:hover{\n            background-color: darkgrey;\n        }\n\n    &lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;div class=\"nav\"&gt;\n        &lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;设为首页&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;手机新浪网&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;移动客户端&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;博客&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;微博&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;关注我&lt;/a&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">块级盒子如何水平居中</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"htm\" spellcheck=\"false\">1. 设置盒子宽度\n2. 盒子左右边距auto， margin: 0 auto;\n</pre>\n<h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">行内元素和行内块元素居中</span></h4>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">给其父元素设置text-align: center;\n</pre>\n<h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">嵌套块元素外边距塌陷问题：</span></h4>\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px; color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 4; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">对于两个嵌套关系的块元素， 父元素有上外边距同时子元素也有上外边距， 此时父元素会塌陷较大的外边距值</span></p>\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px; color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 4; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">解决方法：</span></p>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">1. 给父元素设定上边框 margin-top: 0 solid transparent;\n2. 给父元素设定上内边距\n3. 给父元素设定 overflow: hidden;\n</pre>\n<h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">清除内外边距</span></h4>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"css\" spellcheck=\"false\">*{\n   padding: 0;\n   margin: 0;\n}\n</pre>\n<h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">行内元素尽量只设置左右内边距，块级元素和行内块元素则不需要</span></h4>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">小竖线的制作</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">&lt;em&gt;|&lt;/em&gt;    同时设置font-style: normal\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">注意！ 有些元素可能本身四周就有留白， 因此需要设置这些元素的margin才能正确显示其他盒子的位置</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">border-radius: 10px  圆角边框\nbox-shadow:  10px 10px 10px 10px black | rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n             水平方向 垂直方向  模糊距离  阴影尺寸  阴影颜色 \ntext-shadow: 10px 10px 10px(模糊距离) black;\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">多个块级元素纵向排列找标准流， 横向排列找浮动</span></h3>\n<h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.225; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.75em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; border-bottom-color: #eeeeee; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">浮动</span></h2>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">float: left;\n浮动的盒子不再保留原来的位置\n多个浮动的盒子一行内顶部对齐\n浮动的元素都具有行内块元素的特点，可以设置宽度， 但是如果不设置宽度，宽度跟着内容走\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">浮动的盒子只会影响后面的标准流。</span></h3>\n<h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">当父元素不方便给高度， 就需要清除浮动</span></h4>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">清除浮动</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">1. 父级元素添加overflow:hidden;\n2. after:伪元素\n</pre>\n<h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.225; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.75em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; border-bottom-color: #eeeeee; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">相对定位</span></h2>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">1. 相对于自己原来的位置进行移动\n2. 原来在标准流的位置继续占有， 后面的盒子仍然以标准流的方式对待它\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">绝对定位</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">1. 如果没有祖先节点， 或者说祖先元素没有定位， 则以浏览器为准定位\n2. 如果祖先元素有定位， 则以最近一级的有定位祖先元素为参考点移动位置\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">固定定位</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">固定在版心右侧位置:\n设置好postion: fixed; left: 50%;   margin-left设置为版心宽度一般距离。\n</pre>\n<h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">绝对定位的盒子居中</span></h4>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">left: 50%;\nmargin-left: -自身宽度的一半 ; \n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">绝对定位和固定定位会压住下面标准流的所有内容， 但是浮动元素只会压住下面标准流的盒子， 不会压住盒子里的文字。</span></h3>\n<h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">隐藏和显示</span></h4>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">display: none;\ndisplay: block\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">犯了一个大错， 就是注意是img标签</span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">隐藏案例,鼠标经过有黑色的透明遮罩层</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">&lt;head&gt;\n    &lt;meta charset=\"UTF-8\"&gt;\n    &lt;title&gt;Title&lt;/title&gt;\n    &lt;style&gt;\n        .box{\n            width: 400px;\n            height: 400px;\n            margin: 100px auto;\n            position: relative;\n\n        }\n        .box img{\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n        }\n        .hide{\n            display: none;\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0,0,0, .4) url(arr.png) no-repeat center;\n\n        }\n        .box:hover .hide{\n            display: block;\n        }\n    &lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;div class=\"box\"&gt;\n        &lt;div class=\"hide\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n        &lt;img src=\"tudou.jpg\" alt=\"\"&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n</pre>\n<h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.4; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">a标签没有href属性不能点击的。</span></h4>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">加了绝对定位的盒子可以直接设置高度</span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">定位案例</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\"> &lt;style&gt;\n        *{\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        .box{\n            position: relative;\n            width: 664px;\n            height: 360px;\n            margin: 100px auto;\n        }\n        .box img{\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n        }\n        .lt{\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 0;\n            margin-top: -15px;\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 30px;\n            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n            border-top-right-radius: 15px;\n            border-bottom-right-radius: 15px;\n        }\n        .rt{\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            right: 0;\n            margin-top: -15px;\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 30px;\n            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n        }\n        ul{\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 100px;\n            height: 24px;\n            bottom: 10px;\n            left: 50%;\n            margin-left: -50px;\n            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);\n            border-radius: 12px;\n        }\n        li{\n            list-style: none;\n        }\n        ul li{\n            float: left;\n            width: 8px;\n            height: 8px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background-color: black;\n            margin: 8px 6px;\n        }\n    &lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;div class=\"box\"&gt;\n        &lt;img src=\"tb.jpg\"&gt;\n            &lt;a href=\"#\" class=\"lt\"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;div class=\"rt\"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/div&gt;\n\n        &lt;ul&gt;\n                &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n                &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n                &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n                &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n                &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\n\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">没必要加div就不要加， 注意开头写上margin: 0, padding:0 , 这样后面有一些空白错误就不会遇到。因为很多元素默认是有留白的。</span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">padding应该是设置在父类的盒子里</span></h3>\n<h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.225; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.75em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; border-bottom-color: #eeeeee; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">对照截图来做， 注意放大到百分之百</span></h2>\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px; color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: i