esentation\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"cm-property\">width</span>: <span class=\"cm-number\">200px</span>;</span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"cm-property\">height</span>: <span class=\"cm-number\">200px</span>;</span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"cm-property\">border</span>: <span class=\"cm-number\">1px</span> <span class=\"cm-atom\">solid</span> <span class=\"cm-keyword\">black</span>;</span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"cm-property\">margin-left</span>: <span class=\"cm-number\">-1px</span>;</span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"> &nbsp;  }</span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">style</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-error\">head</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket cm-error\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&lt;</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">body</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&lt;</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">ul</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&lt;</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">li</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">li</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&lt;</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">li</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">li</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&lt;</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">li</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">li</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&lt;</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">li</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">li</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">ul</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span role=\"presentation\"><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"cm-tag\">body</span><span class=\"cm-tag cm-bracket\">&gt;</span></span></pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">实现鼠标移动到li， 四周边框都变色</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">1. 如果li没有定位， 那么在鼠标移动到li，添加相对定位\n2. 如果li有定位， 那么在鼠标移动的li的时候，添加z-index\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">对行内块元素的父元素施加text-align: center, 那么行内块元素和行内元素都会居中对齐</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">&lt;style&gt;\n    .box{\n        text-align: center\n    }\n    a{\n        display: inline-block;\n        list-style: none;\n        border: 2px solid black;\n        background: darkgray;\n        width: 30px;\n        height: 30px;\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-left: 10px;\n    }\n\n&lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;div class=\"box\"&gt;\n        &lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;a href=\"#\"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">直角三角形的实现</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">&lt;style&gt;\n    .box{\n        width: 0;\n        height: 0;\n        border-color: blue red transparent blue;\n        border-style: solid;\n        border-width: 100px 40px 0 0;\n        margin: 100px auto;\n    }\n&lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;div class=\"box\"&gt;\n\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n</pre>\n<h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.225; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.75em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; border-bottom-color: #eeeeee; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">京东css文件初始化</span></h2>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"css\" spellcheck=\"false\">/* 把我们所有标签的内外边距清零 */\n* {\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0\n}\n/* em 和 i 斜体的文字不倾斜 */\nem,\ni {\n    font-style: normal\n}\n/* 去掉li 的小圆点 */\nli {\n    list-style: none\n}\n\nimg {\n    /* border 0 照顾低版本浏览器 如果 图片外面包含了链接会有边框的问题 */\n    border: 0;\n    /* 取消图片底侧有空白缝隙的问题 */\n    vertical-align: middle\n}\n\nbutton {\n    /* 当我们鼠标经过button 按钮的时候，鼠标变成小手 */\n    cursor: pointer\n}\n\na {\n    color: #666;\n    text-decoration: none\n}\n\na:hover {\n    color: #c81623\n}\n\nbutton,\ninput {\n    /* \"\\5B8B\\4F53\" 就是宋体的意思 这样浏览器兼容性比较好 */\n    font-family: Microsoft YaHei, Heiti SC, tahoma, arial, Hiragino Sans GB, \"\\5B8B\\4F53\", sans-serif\n}\n\nbody {\n    /* CSS3 抗锯齿形 让文字显示的更加清晰 */\n    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n    background-color: #fff;\n    font: 12px/1.5 Microsoft YaHei, Heiti SC, tahoma, arial, Hiragino Sans GB, \"\\5B8B\\4F53\", sans-serif;\n    color: #666\n}\n\n.hide,\n.none {\n    display: none\n}\n/* 清除浮动 */\n.clearfix:after {\n    visibility: hidden;\n    clear: both;\n    display: block;\n    content: \".\";\n    height: 0\n}\n\n.clearfix {\n    *zoom: 1\n}\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">html video标签</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">video属性：\n1. autoplay\n2. controls 添加控件\n3. loop  无限循环\n4. poster 预先加载的图片\n5. muted  静音播放， 谷歌需要加上\n</pre>\n<h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.225; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.75em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; border-bottom-color: #eeeeee; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">html audio标签需要加上controls才能显示出来。</span></h2>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">html5新增的表单数据</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">1. required 表示该属性不能为空\n2. autofocus 自动聚焦属性\n3. autocomplete \"off/on\" 显示出历史填写的字段\n4. multiple 可以多选文件提交\n\n//修改颜色\ninput::placeholder{ \ncolor: red; \n}\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">css3新增选择器</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">E[att]         包含att属性\nE[att=\"val\"]    属性是val\nE[att^=\"val\"]  属性以val开头\nE[att$=\"val\"]  属性以val结尾\nE[att*=\"val\"] 属性包含val\n</pre>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\"> //属性选择器举例\n\n&lt;style&gt;\n        input{\n            display: block;\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            margin: 100px auto;\n        }\n            input[type=text]{\n                color: red;\n            }\n\n\n    &lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n&lt;input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"heihei\"&gt;\n&lt;input  placeholder=\"heiheiddddd\"&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n</pre>\n<h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.225; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.75em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; border-bottom-color: #eeeeee; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">css3之伪类选择器</span></h2>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">E:nth-child(n)    //表示选中所有的孩子\nE:nth-child(even) 选中奇数的孩子\n公式  2n : 偶数\n	2n+1 奇数	\n	5n: 5的倍数\n 	n + 5: 从第5个开始\n	-n + 5:  前五个\ndiv div:first-of-type\ndiv div:nth-of-type(1) 找第一个类型为div的，首先是把所有的div按照先后排序\n</pre>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">&lt;div&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;  &lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n对于这种情况 div div:nth-child(1)是找不到任何东西的\n</pre>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">&lt;style&gt;\n    ul li{\n        width: 100px;\n        height: 100px;\n        display: block;\n        background: black;\n    }\n    ul li:first-child{\n        background: red;\n    }\n    ul li:last-child{\n        background: coral;\n    }\n    ul li:nth-child(3){\n        background: yellow;\n    }\n\n\n&lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;ul&gt;\n        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n    &lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n</pre>\n<h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.225; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.75em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; border-bottom-color: #eeeeee; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">伪元素基本使用</span></h2>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">E::before\nE::after\n在该元素内部的前后插入盒子， 这个盒子是行内元素， 没有宽高，\n## 注意必须有content属性，但是这个属性可以为空\n\n&lt;style&gt;\n    div div{\n        color: red;\n        width: 200px;\n        height: 200px;\n        border: 1px solid black;\n        margin-top: 20px;\n    }\n    div div::before{\n        content: \'ee\';\n        display: inline-block;\n        width: 20px;\n        height: 20px;\n        background: yellow;\n        margin-right: 20px;\n    }\n\n&lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;div&gt;\n\n        &lt;div&gt;dd&lt;/div&gt;\n        &lt;div&gt;bb&lt;/div&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n</pre>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">加了绝对定位的盒子可以直接设置宽度和高度</span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">伪元素选择器完成阴影案例</span></h3>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">&lt;style&gt;\n    div{\n        position: relative;\n        width: 300px;\n        height: 200px;\n        background: yellow;\n        margin: 100px auto;\n    }\n    div img{\n        width: 100%;\n        height: 100%;\n    }\n    .tudou::before{\n        display: none;\n        content: \'\';\n        position: absolute;\n        top: 0;\n        left: 0;\n        width: 100%;\n        height: 100%;\n        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n\n    }\n    .tudou:hover::before{\n        display: block;\n    }\n&lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;div class=\"tudou\"&gt;\n        &lt;img src=\"tudou.jpg\" alt=\"\"&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n</pre>\n<h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.225; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.75em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; border-bottom-color: #eeeeee; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">盒子设置， 不再需要人为计算了</span></h2>\n<pre class=\"md-fences mock-cm md-end-block\" lang=\"html\" spellcheck=\"false\">box-sizing: border-box; \n直接放在初始化里\n</pre>\n<h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.225; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Clear Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.75em; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; word-spacing: 0px; border-bottom-color: #eeeeee; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"md-plain\">filter: blur(10px)添加模糊效果</span></h2>\n<h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"color: #333333; text-transform: none; line-height: 1.43; text